{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608700/extras/Main.gif?t=1728057226\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play to the Beat!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Soundfall</strong> is a fast-paced music-based dungeon crawler that combines looter-shooter action with rhythm-based gameplay to create a world of music unlike any other. The closer you time your actions to the rhythm of the soundtrack, the more powerful you become! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Import your own music (PC Only) </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Import your favorite music to create incredible new levels within Symphonia! Available in single player or local co-op play <strong>(not available in online multiplayer)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608700/extras/loadout.gif?t=1728057226\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Thousands of Loot combinations! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock powerful new abilities, and explore Symphonia to discover incredible music-based weaponry! Customize your loadout with more than 500 pieces of equipment to choose from! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Up to 4-Player co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defend Symphonia with your friends, either locally or through online co-op! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>5 characters to choose from!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as one of five unique musical geniuses, each with their own play style, weapon and special abilities! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608700/extras/soundfall-all_characters-600x338.gif?t=1728057226\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Explore the world of music!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore ten dynamically different environments and restore harmony to Symphonia! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1608700/extras/World-600x250.gif?t=1728057226\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DEFEND SYMPHONIA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are a Guardian of Harmony--a musical genius transported to the world of Symphonia by the Composers to battle the forces of Discord. Together with up to four other players, you will fight your way through the corrupted Timbrelands of Symphonia, eradicating the Discordians and restoring Harmony to the environment.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Landed in Symphonia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/fb8179d5d5cc46d058884ff508c473ee26834fa0.jpg"},{"name":"Feeling the Beat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/7f5c17583a763c91d4ee509a5630b6586e0d7d98.jpg"},{"name":"The Sword in the Tone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/3ba88d573c505e8538ea3504467067fc1b408e79.jpg"},{"name":"Breakdown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/2f1277260ae9e45975b490993ce61e8af609bd82.jpg"},{"name":"Record Store","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/806902546020c10a55290bd20029c1f7a6fb490a.jpg"},{"name":"Serenade Skylands","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/f44093eceed156c8ab34dc837b1b68f090f50a19.jpg"},{"name":"Surfbum Thrasher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/c0580dcbaad8bc14b4262b119e18db0890298e6f.jpg"},{"name":"Brass Beach","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1608700/8303a266c46610ab973b6f17b937996b2a836fea.jpg"},{"name":"Classical Prodigy